oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: A Snow Mobile For George Film (undated)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Advertising; Woodcuts (prints); Horses; Cowboys; Restrikes;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (purple and orange on white) advertising A Snow Mobile for George, a film with Buffalo, Fish, Cowboys and Fire Trucks. Poster is undated and features woodcuts of a snow mobile, flames, horses and cowboys. This poster was reprinted in 2008. Posters printed after the original edition are known as "restrikes."
